al beer made with the hops you\'ll see on your ride  <span class=\"divide\">|</span> Pedal past infamous World War II sites in Nuremberg, once the center of the Holy Roman Empire. <i>(Overnight Nuremberg)</i>',1),(1753385,2972,'2','Explore historic Nuremberg and the modern Main-Danube Canal, an engineering marvel','<span class=\"divide\">|</span> Enjoy a laid-back ride through the countryside and picture-perfect medieval towns. <em style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">(Cruise overnight Nuremberg to Kelheim) </em>',2),(1753386,2972,'3','The towers and bridges of Regensburg, a World Heritage site, will take your breath away','<span class=\"divide\">|</span> Bike to the Danube Gorge, a narrow passage carved through rock by the mighty river <span class=\"divide\">|</span> Witness the Porta Praetoria, Germany\'s oldest stone structure. <em>(Cruise overnight Regensburg to Passau)</em>',3),(1753387,2972,'4','Ride in the bucolic border region of Germany and Austria','among hills and river valleys <span class=\"divide\">|</span> Admire Passau\'s splendor on two wheels.<em> (Cruise overnight Linz to Melk)</em>',4),(1753388,2972,'5','Bike or sail through the vineyard-laced Wachau Valley','certain to impress you with its beauty&mdash;and its superb rieslings <span class=\"divide\">|</span> Visit majestic Melk Abbey, quaint towns and traditional <i>Heurigen</i> (wine taverns) <span class=\"divide\">|</span> Ride to enchanting Dürnstein, with its hallmark blue baroque church tower, before an optional evening Mozart and Strauss concert. <i>(Overnight Vienna)</i>',5),(1753389,2972,'6','From St. Stephen\'s Cathedral to the Opera House,','Vienna\'s historic center is magnificent <span class=\"divide\">|</span> Bike along tranquil Danube Island and explore the city on a private walking tour. <em style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">(Cruise overnight Vienna to Budapest)</em>',6),(1753390,2972,'7-8','Be charmed by Budapest during a guided bike tour','<span class=\"divide\">|</span> Treat yourself t