INSERT INTO `statements` VALUES (9243,576,1,'The Best Leaders in Galápagos and the Andes','Backroads has the best-qualified people to lead your trip in Galápagos and the Andes, and our guests back that up, rating our Trip Leaders an average of 9.7 out of 10 for all-around quality of performance. Get the facts (and no fluff) on how we recruit and develop <a href=\"https://www.backroads.com/why/choice/leaders\" target=\"_blank\">the very best people</a> for your trip.','2016-02-01 18:00:38','2016-02-01 18:00:38'),(9244,576,2,'The Right Local Pairings','Our Trip Leaders combine deep local expertise with a firm grasp of North American expectations around quality of service. By the same token, we pair experienced Backroads leaders with local guides who know how to cater to your needs while cracking open the culture or natural history in ways that are meaningful, memorable and often magical.','2016-02-01 18:00:38','2016-02-01 18:00:38'),(9245,576,3,'Experts with Secrets to Share','In choosing the ideal experts to enrich your travel experience, we look for people with a wealth of local knowledge, but also the ability to convey their insights in English. Too often travelers find themselves smiling politely, not quite understanding what they\'re being told. Our experts share intriguing facts, anecdotes and inside stories that stay with you forever.','2016-02-01 18:00:38','2016-02-01 18:00:38'),(9246,576,4,'We Speak the Language','If we told you many companies\' leaders can\'t actually speak the language where they lead trips, you\'d say <em>incroyable</em>... <em>ridicolo</em>... <em>kh&ocirc;ng the tha th&uacute;</em>. At Backroads, fluency in the local language is a given. Find out more on the best leader recruitment, training and development in the business. (And by the way, that was \"unforgivable\" in Vietnamese.) ','2016-02-01 18:00:38','2016-02-01 18:00:38'),(9247,576,5,'Everyone at Their Own Pace','We design and support our Galápagos and the Andes trips to suit mixed abilities and varied interests&mdash;so you can set your own pace, then change things up as the day unfolds. And all guests are free to do the same, traveling together or apart, with no one cramping anyone else\'s style. Which sounds easy in theory, but it\'s hard to pull off. <a href=\"https://www.backroads.com/why/choice/mixed-ability\" target=\"_blank\">Here\'s more</a> on how we do it.','2016-02-01 18:00:38','2016-02-01 18:00:38'),(9248,576,6,'Choose Your Fellow Travelers','With Backroads you won\'t end up with kids on what you thought was an adult trip; we have exclusive departures for families, so they\'re off having their own adventures. As you browse our unrivaled selection of trips and dates, you can count on finding a trip in Galápagos and the Andes that\'s geared exclusively to your choice of traveling companions. ','2016-02-01 18:00:38','2016-02-01 18:00:38'),(9249,576,7,'We\'ve Set the Standard','For nearly four decades we\'ve worked to earn and maintain our right to call Backroads <em>the world\'s #1 active travel company.</em> In pursuing that vision on behalf of our guests, we believe we\'ve set the standard for our industry&mdash;captured in the <a href=\"https://www.backroads.com/quality_index\" target=\"_blank\">Backroads Quality Index</a>, which clearly sets out the benchmarks of excellence, choice and support that we live by. ','2016-02-01 18:00:38','2016-02-01 18:00:38'),(9250,576,8,'Quality You Can Measure','Since 1979, Backroads Founder and President Tom Hale has shown that staying #1 means constantly evaluating our performance using the best possible source of information: our guests. As we systematically analyze your feedback on our trip consultants, leaders, hotels, meals and on-trip activities, we never stop working to make a great company even better.','2016-02-01 18:00:38','2016-02-01 18:00:38'),(9251,576,9,'We Know Where We\'re Going','Tom Hale has been keeping Backroads on track, with one eye on the horizon, since 1979. His passion for active travel, and for ensuring the highest-quality travel experience, is evident in every detail we add to make a guest\'s trip unforgettable&mdash;and the fact he\'s right there in the office, making it happen. To hear Tom describe his vision, <a href=\"https://www.backroads.com/why/philosophy\" target=\"_blank\">watch our video</a>.  ','2016-02-01 18:00:38','2016-02-01 18:00:38'),(9412,873,1,'Leaders Focused on Families','When everyone\'s together, there\'s lots going on; and when kids\' and adults\' priorities diverge, it can seem like two different trips. That\'s why our Family Adventures in Turkey have three Trip Leaders&mdash;including a dedicated Kid Coordinator who regularly takes younger travelers off to do their own thing. Other companies try to get by with two leaders; we step up and do it right. For more on our <a href=\"https://www.backroads.com/familytrips\" target=\"_blank\">family focus</a>, check this out.','2016-02-03 23:15:50','2016-02-03 23:15:50'),(9413,873,2,'Plenty of Kids on Your Trip','It may be hard to imagine being on a family trip with no other families on it&mdash;but it happens regularly with some companies. On a Backroads Family Adventure there are typically several families on each departure, creating more opportunities for your kids to make new friends as they try fun things together &ndash; which is a big part of the experience.','2016-02-03 23:15:50','2016-02-03 23:15:50'),(9414,873,3,'Everyone at Their Own Pace','We design and support our Turkey trips to suit mixed abilities and varied interests&mdash;so you can set your own pace, then change things up as the day unfolds. And all guests are free to do the same, traveling together or apart, with no one cramping anyone else\'s style. Which sounds easy in theory, but it\'s hard to pull off. <a href=\"https://www.backroads.com/why/choice/mixed-ability\" target=\"_blank\">Here\'s more</a> on how we do it.','2016-02-03 23:15:50','2016-02-03 23:15:50'),(9415,873,4,'A Second Van When You Need It','Backroads is the only active travel company providing two support vans in Turkey&mdash;because we know it\'s essential to ensure a truly great travel experience. It doubles our ability to be there when you need us to offer hydration, lighten your load or give you a lift if it\'s time to take a break.  Read more on <a href=\"https://www.backroads.com/why/choice/support_vans\" target=\"_blank\">why two vans</a> make all the difference.','2016-02-03 23:15:50','2016-02-03 23:15:50'),(95721,525,1,'Even Turks Ask Us for Directions','Backroads knows Turkey better than any other active travel company. We\'ve invested over 20 years in researching the best biking routes and developing local relationships, and the result is a rewarding journey that gets you in deep while maintaining our fanatical standards of service. You don\'t want to explore Turkey with guides who are struggling to stay one step ahead of you. Discover this extraordinary country with people who know it inside out.','2016-03-24 18:00:41','2016-03-24 18:00:41'),(95722,525,2,'Everyone at Their Own Pace','We design and support our Turkey trips to suit mixed abilities and varied interests&mdash;so you can set your own pace, then change things up as the day unfolds. And all guests are free to do the same, traveling together or apart, with no one cramping anyone else\'s style. Which sounds easy in theory, but it\'s hard to pull off. <a href=\"https://www.backroads.com/blog/trips-that-let-you-do-it-your-way/\" target=\"_blank\">Here\'s more</a> on how we do it.','2016-03-24 18:00:41','2016-03-24 18:00:41'),(95723,525,3,'A Variety of Routes Each Day','In Turkey you head off each morning after choosing among several expertly designed routes&mdash;all with detailed directions, mileage and shuttle options. Unlike trips with one fixed daily route (or worse, one guide that everyone\'s obliged to follow), you\'re free to enjoy the best of the region at your pace, stopping wherever you want to explore further.','2016-03-24 18:00:41','2016-03-24 18:00:41'),(95724,525,4,'More Leaders to Support You','On our Turkey trips we have an extra leader supporting you along the road&mdash;for a total of three, compared to the industry standard two. So we can be in more places at once, giving personal attention to guests traveling at their own pace. Here\'s more on our <a href=\"https://www.backroads.com/why/choice/leaders\" target=\"_blank\">Trip Leaders</a>.','2016-03-24 18:00:41','2016-03-24 18:00:41'),(95725,525,5,'Experts with Secrets to Share','In choosing the ideal experts to enrich your travel experience, we look for people with a wealth of local knowledge, but also the ability to convey their insights in English. Too often travelers find themselves smiling politely, not quite understanding what they\'re being told. Our experts share intriguing facts, anecdotes and inside stories that stay with you forever.','2016-03-24 18:00:41','2016-03-24 18:00:41'),(95726,525,6,'The Best Leaders in Turkey','Backroads has the best-qualified people to lead your trip in Turkey, and our guests back that up, rating our Trip Leaders an average of 9.7 out of 10 for all-around quality of performance. Get the facts (and no fluff) on how we recruit and develop <a href=\"https://www.backroads.com/why/choice/leaders\" target=\"_blank\">the very best people</a> for your trip.','2016-03-24 18:00:41','2016-03-24 18:00:41'),(95727,525,7,'Only the Best Hotels','On this Premiere Inn trip, you can count on the best lodgings Turkey has to offer. In fact, the hotels we\'ve chosen in this region have higher retail room rates than those offered by any other active travel company&mdash;even when their trips cost more.','2016-03-24 18:00:41','2016-03-24 18:00:41'),(95728,525,8,'We\'ve Set the Standard','For nearly four decades we\'ve worked to earn and maintain our right to call Backroads <em>the world\'s #1 active travel company.</em> In pursuing that vision on behalf of our guests, we believe we\'ve set the standard for our industry&mdash;captured in the <a href=\"https://www.backroads.com/quality_index\" target=\"_blank\">Backroads Quality Index</a>, which clearly sets out the benchmarks of excellence, choice and support that we live by. ','2016-03-24 18:00:41','2016-03-24 18:00:41'),(95729,525,9,'In Europe Since 1988','Backroads has been welcoming active travelers to Europe since before the Berlin Wall came down. Today it\'s virtually our second home. We know the perfect roads and trails, the most scenic valleys and hilltop towns, the hidden churches and gem-like museums, the up-and-coming vintners and celebrated chefs&mdash;and, of course, all the best places to stay.','2016-03-24 18:00:41','2016-03-24 18:00:41'),(95730,525,10,'Our Cultural Roots Run Deep','Thanks to our extensive connections in Turkey, Backroads takes you off the beaten track and deep into the region\'s culture in ways that traditional travel can never hope to do. We know the people and their customs, the legacy of art and architecture, the complex history and politic&mdash;and if we\'re not sure, our amazing local experts can fill in the blanks. ','2016-03-24 18:00:42','2016-03-24 18:00:42'),(95731,525,11,'Navigate Your Way in Turkey','Your ride comes equipped with a Garmin Edge Explore 1000, the best bike-touring GPS device on the market. This is a Backroads exclusive, and it\'s included with your bike in Turkey. If you prefer to bring your own device, we also have downloadable GPS files and of course, our good old paper directions are always available. Read more on why our <a href=\"https://www.backroads.com/blog/navigating-into-the-future\" target=\"_blank\">navigation options</a> are the best. ','2016-03-24 18:00:42','2016-03-24 18:00:42'),(95732,525,12,'Great Bikes Included (or Upgrade)','Choose a Backroads Custom Titanium or Custom Electric Assist bike&mdash;both are included in your trip price. Maybe a Specialized carbon-fiber pro model is more your speed or go for double fun on a tandem. Our 