INSERT INTO `trips` VALUES (501,'Canadian Rockies Bike Tour \n','Epic Landscapes & Endless Ice Fields from Banff to Jasper',0,'Banff, Alberta','Banff, Alberta','','Just sky, water, rock and wheels. Glaciated peaks soaring above the trees. Air that feels like the purest you\'ve ever breathed. A mountain-lined parkway you\'ll ride the entire day. Bighorn sheep. Lake Louise, simply stunning. The Post Hotel&mdash;flawless luxury in such a rugged land. Your ride is simplicity, rawness and beauty in its truest form.&#8193;','Banff, Jasper, National Park, Lake Louise, biking, canoe, Athabasca Glacier, float trip, biking, bike trip, bike tour, bike vacation, biking vacation, bicycle tour, bicycle trip, bicycling vacation, Canadian Rockies, cycling, cycle, Canada','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BCNI_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BCNI_16_map_lg.jpg','Canadian Rockies Map','Canadian Rockies Vacations','Canadian Rockies Map','Canadian Rockies Vacations','\n<ul>\n    <li>A vast wilderness of magnificent peaks, massive glaciers, pristine mountain lakes and broad valleys\n    <li>Spectacular Lake Louise\n    <li>Ride the Icefields Parkway, a journey through the heart of the Canadian Rockies\n    <li>Incredibly crisp clean mountain air\n    <li>The Post Hotel, blending old-world charm with modern sophistication </li>\n</ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/BCNI-canadian-rockies-bike-tour.jpg'),(525,'Turkey Bike Tour \n','A Cultural Odyssey along the Mediterranean Coast',0,'Bodrum, Turkey','Dalaman, Turkey','','Great getaways don\'t just remove you from the day-to-day&mdash;they rejuvenate you. That\'s our trip in Turkey. Explore the friendly Turkish coast, splitting your nights between lovely hotels and a Turkish <em>gulet</em>, serenely floating on the Mediterranean. Pedal past pine forests and olive groves, then spend evenings stargazing. It\'s a vacation on your vacation.','biking, Turkey, bike, bicycle, cycle, cycling, tour, trip, vacation, active vacation, adventure, Europe biking tour','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BTKI_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BTKI_16_map_lg.jpg','Turkey Europe Map','Turkey Biking','Turkey Europe Map','Turkey Biking Vacations','\n<ul>\n    <li>Experience the crossroads of East and West\n    <li>Rides through pine-dappled hills, olive groves, craggy outcrops, sunny beaches and friendly villages\n    <li>The ancient ruins of Knidos and Kaunos \n    <li>Break bread with a Turkish family at their traditional home\n    <li>Sail the Mediterranean in traditional wooden <i>gulets,</i> dropping anchor to swim, snorkel and slumber </li>\n</ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/BTKI-turkey-bike-tour.jpg'),(536,'Czech Republic & Austria Bike Tour \n','Bohemia & the Wachau Valley from Prague to Vienna',0,'Prague, Czech Republic','Vienna, Austria','','Has the 21st century gone missing? Look around. It seems as if time has stopped among half-timbered villages almost too quaint to be real. Amid storybook countryside and alongside a mighty river. Explore Austria\'s splendid Wachau Valley and an undiscovered corner of the Czech Republic. We hope it stays this way forever.','Czech Republic, Austria, biking, bike trip, bike tour, bike vacation, biking vacation, bicycle tour, bicycle trip, bicycling vacation,','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BZAI_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BZAI_16_map_lg.jpg','Czech Republic Map','Czech Republic & Austria Biking','Czech Republic Map','Czech Republic Biking Vacations','<ul><li>An inspiring journey that bridges must-see regions of two captivating countries</li><li>Raise a toast to the local culture&mdash;taste superb Austrian wines and some of the best beers in the world!</li><li>Sensational gateway cities&mdash;Prague and Vienna&mdash;may tempt you to extend your vacation</li><li>Our local friends become yours as they offer thoughtful insight on regional traditions, history and daily life</li><li>Your table awaits&mdash;enjoy the best dining experiences we offer in the Czech Republic and Austria</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/BZAI-czech-republic-austria-bike-tour.jpg'),(545,'Galapagos & Andes Multi-Adventure Tour','Ecuador\'s Magical Peaks & Wildlife\n',0,'Cotacachi, Ecuador','Quito, Ecuador','','As you delve into pre-Inca history, rub shoulders with Andean indigenous peoples, commune with condors, hike a volcano\'s rim, snorkel with sea lions, and encounter blue-footed boobies and giant tortoises, you\'ll realize that something has happened. You\'ve been forever changed by Ecuador\'s amazing Andes and islands.','Ecuador, Galapagos Islands, biking, hiking, bike tour, walking vacation, hike trip, latin america, highlands, andes, bicycling trip, bicycle tour','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MECQ_16_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/18-map-MECI.jpg','Ecuador and Galapagos Multisport Map','Ecuador Multisport','Ecuador and Galapagos Multisport Map','Galapagos & Andes multisport tour thumb','<ul><li><strong>Hike </strong>a caldera rim in the Andes with spectacular views of snowcapped volcanoes and deep-blue lakes</li><li><strong>Bike </strong>to white-sand beaches and explore small highland villages where indigenous people continue centuries-old traditions</li><li><strong>Learn</strong> from an expert local guide during close encounters with Galápagos wildlife&mdash;a once-in-a-lifetime experience!</li><li><strong>Discover</strong> unique species snorkeling and kayaking with tropical fish, sea lions, white-tipped reef sharks, sea turtles and beloved blue-footed boobies</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MECI-galapagos-andes-multi-adventure-tour-1.jpg'),(562,'Mexico\'s Yucatán Multi-Adventure Tour','Chichen Itza & the Maya Riviera',0,'Mérida, Mexico','Cancún, Mexico','','Beautiful Caribbean beaches, colonial towns and the magnificent legacy of the Maya civilization. Azure waters rife with tropical fish, ideal for snorkeling. The enigmatic ruins at Chichén Itzá, one of the new Seven Wonders of the World. Quiet bike routes. Hidden swimming holes. Exquisite hotels and unforgettable cuisine. The Maya Riviera is waiting for you<i>. ¡Vamos!</i>','','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/19-map-MYCI.svg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/20_MYCI.jpg','Yucatán Multi-Adventure Tour | Map','Yucatán Multi-Adventure Tour','Yucatan Mexico Map','Mexico Yucatán Multi-Adventure Tour','<ul><li><strong>Celebrate </strong>Maya history, Mexican traditions and a vibrant modern culture on the endlessly interesting Yucatán Peninsula</li><li><strong>Hike</strong> through otherworldly caves, kayak through lush mangroves, swim in natural blue pools and snorkel in the Caribbean Sea</li><li><strong>Bike</strong> quiet rural roads to the fascinating Maya town of Izamal, and to Valladolid, a colonial city turned artisan hot spot</li><li><strong>Bask</strong> in the dazzling colors of the region, the incredible flavors of its cuisine, the welcoming people and the warm sun on the Maya Riviera</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MYCI-yucatan-multiadventure-tour-2.jpg'),(572,'Costa Rica Walking & Hiking Tour','Caribbean Lowlands, Arenal Volcano & Pacific Coast',0,'San José, Costa Rica','Liberia, Costa Rica','','Experience Costa Rica\'s colors. The surreal aquamarine of the Río Celeste. Flashes of sapphire and ruby-red from motmots and hummingbirds. Emerald-green jungle with glimmers of golden orchids and opalescent butterflies. Costa Rica has been called the jewel of Central America&mdash;you should see this gem up close.','Costa Rica, hiking tour, walking trip, walking vacation, walking tour, walk, hike, Arenal volcano, cloud forest, rain forest, nature hike','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/WCRI_16_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/WCRI_17_map_lg.jpg','Costa Rica Map','Costa Rica Walking','Costa Rica Map','Costa Rica Walking Hiking Tours','<ul><li>Turquoise Río Celeste and its spectacular waterfall</li><li>Get a taste of Tico life on hikes through the countryside and while sharing a meal with our local friends</li><li>Boat across Lake Arenal, with magnificent Arenal Volcano always on the horizon</li><li>Spot howler monkeys, sloths and toucans as you traverse the rain forest on a network of hanging bridges</li><li>Beautiful beaches and stunning coastline await in Guanacaste Province</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/WCRI-costarica-walking-hiking-tour.jpg'),(576,'Galapagos & Andes Walking & Hiking Tour \n','Darwin\'s Enchanted Islands & the Ecuadorian Highlands\n',0,'Cotacachi, Ecuador','Quito, Ecuador','','Epic scenery, rich traditions and welcoming highland people. And of course, those incredible islands, where tortoises lumber and blue-footed boobies dance. In Ecuador, it\'s not just the thin Andes air that leaves you breathless. To experience this land firsthand is to feel a sense of wonder in one of the last great wild places.','Galapagos Islands, walking, hiking, hike, walk, trip, tour, vacation, Ecuador, nature, wildlife, walking tour, hiking tour, Andes','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/WECI_16_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/WECI_16_map_lg.jpg','Ecuador Map','Ecuador Walking Tour','Ecuador Map','Ecuador Galapagos Walking Hiking Vacations','\n<ul>\n    <li>Explore highland villages, where Otavaleño Indians continue centuries-old traditions\n    <li>Connect with one of Ecuador\'s foremost master weavers during a tour of his studio\n    <li>Visit award-winning Condor Huasi, a rehabilitation center for Andean condors\n    <li>Get set for a life-altering experience as you view Galápagos wildlife up close with an expert local guide\n    <li>Swim and snorkel with sea lions and, yes, even with white-tipped reef sharks! </li>\n</ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/WECI-ecuador-walking-hiking-tour.jpg'),(593,'Tuscany Walking & Hiking Tour \n','Ancient Footpaths in Medieval Italy \n',0,'Florence, Italy','Florence, Italy','','Tuscany must be experienced up close. Taste the Brunello. See the bread toasted in a stone fireplace, glistening with freshly pressed olive oil. Stroll through vineyards and hilltop towns. Let your eyes linger on ancient villas. Imagine the possibilities. There is no better&mdash;or closer&mdash;way to experience Tuscany.','Tuscany Walking, Italy hiking tour, hiking, hike tour, trip, vacation, Italian countryside, walking, walk trip, cooking, cuisine, italian food, wine tasting,','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/WTCI_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/WTCI_16_map_lg.jpg','Tuscany Italy Map','Tuscany Walking Vacations','Tuscany Italy Map','Tuscany Walking Vacations','<ul><li>Unforgettable rambles though the Chianti Classico wine region, blanketed with vineyards and olive orchards</li><li>Enjoy a warm welcome at Agriturismo Il Rigo for an authentic pasta making demonstration</li><li>Discover the World Heritage site of Siena, where medieval architecture meets contemporary culture</li><li>Explore classic hill towns including Pienza, Radda, Panzano and San Gimignano</li><li>Join a wine expert to sample a variety of the San Felice estate wines and other regional vintages</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/WTCI-tuscany-walking-hiking-tour-7.jpg'),(623,'Tuscany Family Bike Tour \n','The Heart of Italy, from Umbria to Chianti',0,'Chiusi, Italy','Florence, Italy','','Tuscany is not a destination. It\'s a sublime experience. Routes lined with cypress trees. Patchwork vineyards. And no view will compare to that view. Until you round the next bend and see another. And that\'s only what you\'ll see; imagine the wines, the multitude of gelato flavors and the luxuries you\'ll discover.','Tuscany, biking tour, bike trip, bike tour, bike vacation, biking vacation, bicycle tour, bicycle trip, bicycling vacation, bicycle tour Italy, Chianti bike tour, biking in Italy','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BTTIF_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BTTIF_16_map_lg.jpg','Tuscany Italy Map','Tuscany Biking Tour','Tuscany Italy Map','Tuscany Biking Vacations','<ul><li>Savor every fun-filled moment of this favorite Backroads family trip</li><li>Pedal rolling hills and quiet roads&mdash;scenic kid-approved routes with ample shuttle support</li><li>Soak up the Tuscan sun in classic Renaissance towns like Cortona and magical Montepulciano</li><li>Pizza, gelato, fresh pasta, cheese and acclaimed regional wines... delicious flavors for palates of all ages</li><li>A scavenger hunt, ceramics painting and a falconry demonstration are sure to captivate the younger set</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/BTTIF-tuscany-bike-tour.jpg'),(637,'Bryce, Zion & Grand Canyon Multisport Adventure Tour','Adventures in the Incredible Canyons of Utah & Arizona \n',0,'St. George, Utah','St. George, Utah','','Three national parks. Six glorious days. Countless ways to enjoy the outdoors. This trip will have you biking, hiking and camping in one of North America\'s most stunning regions&mdash;and sharing the fun with a fantastic bunch of like-minded travelers. Come join the friendliest group of adventurers around, and get set for good times!','Bryce Canyon, Zion Canyon, Grand Canyon, biking trip, bike tour, hiking tour, walking vacation, national park, camping, singles tour, solos trip','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MBGC_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MBGC_16_map_lg.jpg','Bryce Zion Map','Utah Multisport Vacations','Bryce Zion Utah Map','Utah Multisport Vacations','\n<ul>\n    <li>Dramatic vistas of petrified sand dunes, sculpted hoodoos and river-chiseled gorges\n    <li>Hike past Bryce Canyon\'s celebrated spires and pinnacles\n    <li>Contemplate the humbling vastness of the Grand Canyon\n    <li>Follow a path as it snakes up the side of a cliff in Zion Canyon\n    <li>Enjoy campsites perched on canyon rims and under the cool canopy of towering pines </li>\n</ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MBGC-bryce-zion-grandcanyon-multisport-tour.jpg'),(645,'Death Valley Multisport Adventure Tour','California\'s Desert Wonderland  \n',0,'Las Vegas, Nevada','Las Vegas, Nevada','','The names are ominous. Death Valley. Badwater. Yet there\'s striking beauty. And opportunity for great pleasure. The rippling sand dunes. Colorful mountains. Plants and animals thriving amid topographic extremes. Now you\'re one of them. Savoring the views. Tackling the rides. And basking in the sun. With nothing but good omens in sight.','biking, National Park, Great Salt Flats, desert, california, bike trip, bike tour, bike vacation, Death Valley, hiking tour, walking trip','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BCDQ_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MCDQ_16_map_lg.jpg','California Deserts Map','Death Valley Multisport Tour','','Death Valley Multisport Vacations','<ul><li>Bike across salt flats to the lowest point in the US</li><li>Explore 100-foot-high sand dunes at Mesquite Flat</li><li>Have a look around the ghost town of Rhyolite, then bike down the valley with views of sand dunes and the Panamint Mountain Range</li><li>Hike through Golden Canyon to behold famous Zabriskie Point</li><li>Savor the tranquility of the desert as you relax under the palms at the Inn at Furnace Creek\'s spring-fed pool</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MCDQ-deathvalley-multisport-tour.jpg'),(648,'Costa Rica Multisport Adventure Tour \n','Cloud Forest, Arenal Volcano & the Pacific Coast',0,'San José, Costa Rica','San José, Costa Rica','','Like wildlife and outdoor adventure? You\'ll love Costa Rica, where monkeys enliven the canopy and iguanas bask in the sun. Jungle hikes, bike rides and kayaking immerse you in extraordinary biodiversity, from Los Angeles Cloud Forest to Arenal Volcano National Park and the Pacific coast. Get set to have fun, relax and discover your own <i>pura vida</i>!','Costa Rica, biking, hiking, rafting, kayaking, bike tour, biking trip, hiking vacation, active travel, Backroads, Arenal Volcano, adventure tour','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MCRQ_16_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MCRQ_16_map_lg.jpg','Costa Rica Map','Costa Rica Multisport','Costa Rica Map','Costa Rica Multisport Vacations','\n<ul>\n    <li>Commune with nature at the tranquil eco-friendly Villa Blanca Cloud Forest Hotel\n    <li>Relax in the hot springs of a forest hideaway while watching for signs of life from the volcano\n    <li>Explore Lake Arenal and the surrounding rain forest by boat and bike\n    <li>Observe a stunning variety of wildlife - sloths, monkeys, lizards and more - in Manuel Antonio National Park\n    <li>Kayak across crystalline waters to a beautiful remote beach </li>\n</ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MCRQ-costa-rica-multisport-tour-2.jpg'),(653,'Galapagos & Andes Family Multi-Adventure Tour &ndash; Teens & Kids','Ecuador\'s Ancient Culture & Wondrous Wildlife',0,'Cotacachi, Ecuador','Quito, Ecuador','','Hike to villages in volcano-studded highlands and discover crafts, music and ancient ruins. Then enjoy a mind-blowing adventure in the Galápagos Islands. Ever see a frigate bird strut his stuff? Or a seaweed-eating iguana? Alongside a naturalist, witness incredible wildlife behavior right before your eyes.','Galapagos, Ecuador, Galapagos Islands, biking, hiking, walking tour, kayaking tour, vacation, trip, family vacation, family tour, family activel trave, bike tour, hiking vacation, mutisport','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MECQF_16_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/18-map-MECIF.jpg','Ecuador and Galapagos family trip map','Ecuador Family Multisport','Ecuador and Galapagos map','Galapagos & Andes Multisport','<ul><li><strong>Hike </strong>in the Andes with views of snowcapped mountains and visit an award-winning rehabilitation center for Andean condors</li><li><strong>Explore</strong> small, indigenous highland villages, where centuries-old traditions are still thriving</li><li><strong>Captivate</strong> the kids with activities like building Andean pan flutes, milking a cow, weaving with a local artist and making a special Galápagos craft</li><li><strong>Snorkel</strong> and kayak with tropical fish, sea lions and white-tipped reef sharks in the Galápagos&mdash;a once-in-a-lifetime experience!</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MECIF-galapagos-andes-multi-adventure-tour-1.jpg'),(659,'Canadian Rockies Multisport Adventure Tour \n','Bike, Walk & Raft in Banff & Jasper National Parks \n',0,'Banff, Alberta','Banff, Alberta','','Camp with us in the Canadian Rockies and add some ahhhh to your life. Wake to the sound of birdsong. Be lured from your tent by the aroma of fresh coffee and the sight of peaks and glaciers towering above you. In the evening, tell tales and laugh around the campfire. Wrap yourself in a blanket of stars. Ahhhh.','Candian Rockies, biking tour, Banff, Jasper, National Park, raft trip, bike tour, hiking trip, singles tour, solos vacation, camping trip','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MJBC_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MJBC_16_map_lg.jpg','Jasper Banff Canada Map','Canadian Rockies Tour','Jasper Banff Canada Map','Canadian Rockies Multisport Vacations','<ul><li>Soak up sensational views as you ride along the Bow Valley Parkway</li><li>Walk on massive Athabasca Glacier with informative mountain guides</li><li>Terrific company, the warmth of a campfire and the beauty of a star-filled sky</li><li>Float Class II rapids of the Athabasca River</li><li>A wealth of wildlife&mdash;look for deer, moose, elk and black bears</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MJBC-canadianrockies-multisport-tour.jpg'),(660,'Canadian Rockies Family Multisport Adventure Tour','A Peak Experience in Banff & Jasper National Parks',0,'Banff, Alberta','Banff, Alberta','','It\'s just plain cool. Walking on a massive river of ice. Not just you&mdash;the whole family is there. Rafting is next. Rock climbing tomorrow. Maybe an elk will visit camp tonight. And you\'ll get up the nerve to jump in the lake. And s\'mores will be for dessert. But right now you\'re on top of a glacier. Talk about cool.','biking, rafting, hiking, bike tour, trip, vacation, Banff, Jasper, National Park, raft trip, horseback riding, camping vacation, family trip','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MJBCF_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MJBCF_16_map_lg.jpg','Banff Jasper Canada Map','Canadian Rockies Family','Banff Jasper Canada Map','Canadian Rockies Family Vacations','\n<ul>\n    <li>Natural and historic treasures discovered by foot and bike\n    <li>Walk on massive Athabasca Glacier with informative mountain guides\n    <li>Crackling campfires and star-filled skies\n    <li>Float Class II rapids on the Athabasca River\n    <li>Kids rock climb with accredited instructors </li>\n</ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MJBCF-canadianrockies-multisport-tour.jpg'),(667,'New Zealand Family Multisport Adventure Tour \n','Family Fun on the North Island \n',0,'Auckland, New Zealand','Taupo, New Zealand','','Kiwis know how to have serious fun. Supercharged hiking, biking and boating. Discovering giant tree ferns, percolating mud pots, gorgeous gorges, dramatic coastline and hidden swimming holes&mdash;it\'s all just part of the daily grind. Don\'t miss out on the fun!','New Zealand, biking, hiking, rafting, kyaking, walking tour, vacation, trip, cycling tour, cycle, bicycling vacation, family tour, family adventure vacation, North Island','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MNZIF_16_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MNZIF_16_map_lg.jpg','New Zealand Map','New Zealand Family','New Zealand Map','New Zealand Family Vacations','<ul><li>Bike past Rotorua\'s fascinating geothermal elements to hot springs perfect for a soak</li><li>Experience traditional Maori customs and foods at a <i>marae</i> (ceremonial meeting place)</li><li>Shoot the rapids of the Tongariro River</li><li>Stroll past giant tree ferns and hanging vines to a secret valley</li><li>Kayak on Lake Rotoiti to a small hot spring accessible only by boat</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MNZIF-new-zealand-multisport-tour-9.jpg'),(679,'Mexico\'s Yucatán Family Multi-Adventure Tour - Kids & Teens','Jungles, Beaches & Ancient Maya Pyramids',0,'Mérida, Mexico','Cancún, Mexico','','Experience an exciting family adventure in Mexico\'s Yucatán, from ancient pyramids to white-sand <i>playas</i>. Discover remnants of the Maya kingdom on a visit to Chichén Itzá, one of the new Seven Wonders of the World. Then explore a brilliant underwater empire with a mask and snorkel in the warm Caribbean Sea. Hike jungle trails, bike to colonial towns, play on picture-perfect beaches and take a siesta at exquisite hotel hideaways. This family vacation rules.','','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/19-map-MYCI.svg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/20_MYCIF.jpg','Mexico Yucatán Family Multi-Adventure Tour Map','Mexico','Yucatan Mexico Map','Mexico Yucatan Family Multi-Adventure Tour - Teens & Kids','<ul><li><strong>Celebrate</strong> Maya history, Mexican traditions and a vibrant modern culture on the endlessly interesting Yucatán Peninsula</li><li><strong>Adventure</strong> with your family through caves, bike past ancient ruins, swim in azure pools and snorkel in the Caribbean Sea</li><li><strong>Sway</strong> in a hammock at one of the area\'s best hotels or to the tune of a classic Mexican melody played by a local <i>guitarrista </i>(guitarist)</li><li><strong>Bask</strong> in the dazzling colors of the region, the incredible flavors of its cuisine, the welcoming people and the warm Maya Riviera sun</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MYCI-yucatan-multiadventure-tour-1.jpg'),(777,'Provence Bike Tour \n','From Les Alpil