.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/BTKIF-turkey-bike-tour.jpg'),(2926,'Berlin to Dresden Family Bike Tour \n','Dynamic Cities & Idyllic Countryside',0,'Berlin, Germany\n','Dresden, Germany\n','','Experience Germany\'s story. Ride a treelined trail along the course of the former Berlin Wall. Admire the splendor of Dresden, once known as \"Florence on the Elbe.\" Bike amid dense woodlands, old-world towns and quiet waterways. The culture, the cuisine, the history, the hospitality. Germany\'s story from a fresh perspective: your family\'s own.','Germany bike tour, Berlin bike tours, Dresden cycling tour, bicycle tour, Europe biking, cycling vacation','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BDBIF_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BDBIF_17_map_lg.jpg','Berlin and Dresden Map','Berlin and Dresden Family biking trip','Berlin and Dresden biking map','Berlin and Desden family bike tour thumb','<ul><li>Experience Germany from every angle: countryside biking, urban exploration, cultural discoveries and culinary delights</li><li>Discover the World Heritage site of Potsdam and the extraordinary Biosphere Reserve of Spreewald</li><li>Incredible Michelin-starred dining fit for a king at Bayrisches Haus</li><li>Raise a glass of Riesling to the Elbe Valley\'s 800-year-old winemaking history</li><li>Captivating gateway cities of Berlin and Dresden&mdash;ideal to visit before or after your trip</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/BDBIF-berlin-dresden-bike-tour.jpg'),(2939,'Tuscany & Umbria Family Bike Tour - Older Teens & 20s','The Land of the Renaissance from Rome to Florence',0,'Arezzo, Italy','Florence, Italy','','No doubt you\'ll arrive with certain expectations of Tuscany and Umbria. But somehow the sensory feast is still a wonderful surprise. The sheer beauty of olive groves and vineyards. The slow pace of life. The symphony of fla