ver, surrounded by lush aquatic vegetation and watching for toucans in the trees</li><li>Stroll the white-sand shores of Playa Blanca or snorkel and swim in the Caribbean</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MPAI9-panama-multisport-tour-2.jpg'),(2966,'Mekong River Cruise Bike Tour','The Allure of Cambodia & Vietnam',0,'Siem Reap, Cambodia','Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam','','It\'s a place of intriguing contrasts: exotic silks and down-to-earth rice farmers. Raw jungles and floating markets. Bustling cities and ancient temples. You might see a monk on a smartphone one moment and a family of six on a moped the next. Let the river be your guide to this mysterious lifeline of South East Asia.','Mekong River, river cruise bike tour, biking trip, Vietnam, Cambodia, cycling tour, active travel, river cruising, cycling adventure, cycle trip','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BMKS_16_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BMKS_16_map_lg.jpg','Mekong River Cruise Bike Tour Map','Mekong River Cruise Bike Tour','Mekong River Cruise Bike Tour Map','Mekong River Cruise Bike Tour','<ul><li>Sail and bike along one of the world\'s most captivating rivers</li><li>Marvel at Indochina\'s beauty, from the Khmer carvings at Angkor Wat to welcoming monks</li><li>Let us open doors to reveal the rich local traditions, landscapes and lifestyles</li><li>Pedal quiet roads past bucolic villages, vibrant green rice paddies and floating markets</li><li>Lose yourself among the sights, sounds and flavors of two distinct countries and cultures</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/BMKS-mekong-river-cruise-bike-tour.jpg'),(2967,'Colombia Walking & Hiking Tour','From Bogotá to the Coffee Triangle & Cartagena',0,'Bogotá, Colombia','Cartagena, Colombia','','It\'s all amazing. All the way from the verdant Cocora