retches</li><li>Visit the German town of Koblenz, medieval Strasbourg and impeccably preserved Riquewihr</li><li>Bike the Route des Vins in Alsace, perhaps stopping to taste world-class gewürztraminers and rieslings</li><li>Cruise through the picturesque Rhine Gorge, admiring its multitude of fortress ruins and castles</li><li>Explore at your own pace and in your own personal style&mdash;our river cruise itineraries offer the ultimate flexibility!</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/BRIS9-rhine-river-cruise-bike-tour.jpg'),(3000,'Palm Springs & Joshua Tree Bike Tour','Desert Drama in Southern California',0,'Palm Springs, California','Palm Springs, California','','In the desert, less is more. A single white cloud stands out in the vast blue sky. Joshua trees take center stage against the infinite landscape. Shady spots feel even more welcome in the arid warmth of the sun. Here, in stark contrast to the outside world, the real beauty is not found in what is&#133; but what isn\'t.','bike tour, biking trip, Palm Springs, Joshua Tree National Park, cycling vacation, biking tour','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BPJI_16_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BPJI_16_map_lg.jpg','Palm Springs and Joshua Tree Bike Tour Map','Palm Springs and Joshua Tree bike tour','Palm Springs and Joshua Tree bike tour map','Palm Springs and Joshua Tree Bike Tour','<ul><li>In Joshua Tree National Park, pedal remote roads amid gravity-defying rock formations and the namesake flora</li><li>Visit galleries, boutiques and cafés in lively Palm Springs</li><li>Bike to a hidden palm oasis, home to desert wildlife like roadrunners and bighorn sheep</li><li>Luxuriate at splendid hotels&mdash;two elegant desert retreats with rave-worthy spas</li><li>Marvel at sweeping desert vistas while aboard the famous Palm Springs Aerial Tramway</li></ul>','https:/