s towering above you. In the evening, tell tales and laugh around the campfire. Wrap yourself in a blanket of stars. Ahhhh.','Candian Rockies, biking tour, Banff, Jasper, National Park, raft trip, bike tour, hiking trip, singles tour, solos vacation, camping trip','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MJBC_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MJBCB_16_map_lg.jpg','Jasper Banff Canada Map','Canadian Rockies Tour','Jasper Banff Canada Map','Canadian Rockies Multisport Vacations','<ul><li>Soak up sensational views as you ride along the Bow Valley Parkway</li><li>Walk on massive Athabasca Glacier with informative mountain guides</li><li>Terrific company, the warmth of a campfire and the beauty of a star-filled sky</li><li>Float Class II rapids of the Athabasca River</li><li>A wealth of wildlife&mdash;look for deer, moose, elk and black bears</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MJBCB-banff-jasper-multisport-tour.jpg'),(3026,'Zion & Snow Canyon Multisport Adventure Tour \n','Southwest Utah\'s Red-Rock Splendor \n',0,'Ivins, Utah','St. George, Utah \n','','Sculpted over hundreds of millions of years. Snow Canyon and Zion reveal the depths of geologic time with dramatic clarity. Soaring sandstone walls and monoliths. Deep fissures and vast mesas. All in a palette of pinks, reds and oranges too brilliant to believe. It\'s a boundless panorama of geologic eye candy. With the power to spellbind.','Snow Canyon State Park, Zion National Park, bike tour, biking vacation, cycling trip, hiking tour, walking vacation, Narrows, Angel\'s Landing','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MZII_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MZIQ_16_map_lg.jpg','Zion and Snow Canyon Multisport Tour Map','Snow Canyon Main Photo','','Zion and Snow Canyon Multisport thumb','<ul><li>Sand dunes, cinder cones and towering sandstone cliffs in Snow Canyon State Park</li><li>Follow part of the St. George Ironman route on your way to Gunlock State Park</li><li>Trek through the Narrows in Zion, one of the most unique routes you\'ll experience </li><li>A thrilling hike to Angels Landing, bringing you nearly 1,500 feet above the valley</li><li>Bike along car-free Zion Canyon Scenic Drive</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MZIQ-zion-snow-canyon-multisport-tour.jpg'),(3054,'Galapagos & Andes Family Multi-Adventure Tour &ndash; Older Teens & 20s','Ecuador\'s Magical Peaks & Wildlife\n',0,'Cotacachi, Ecuador','Quito, Ecuador','','As you and your family delve into pre-Inca history, rub shoulders with Andean indigenous peoples, commune with condors, hike a volcano\'s rim, snorkel with sea lions, and encounter blue-footed boobies and giant tortoises, you\'ll realize that something has happened. You\'ve been forever changed by Ecuador\'s amazing Andes and islands.','Ecuador, Galapagos Islands, biking, hiking, bike tour, walking vacation, hike trip, latin america, highlands, andes, bicycling trip, bicycle tour','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/MECQB_16_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/18-map-MECIB.jpg','Ecuador and Galapagos Multisport Map','Ecuador Multisport','Ecuador and Galapagos Multisport Map','Galapagos & Andes multisport tour thumb','<ul><li><strong>Hike </strong>a caldera rim in the Andes with spectacular views of snowcapped volcanoes and deep-blue lakes and bike to white-sand beaches</li><li><strong>Explore</strong> small highland villages where indigenous people continue centuries-old traditions</li><li><strong>Learn</strong> alongside an expert local guide during amazingly close encounters with Galápagos wildlife&mdash;a once-in-a-lifetime experience!</li><li><strong>Discover</strong> unique species and marine life as you snorkel and kayak with tropical fish, sea lions, sea turtles and the beloved blue-footed boobies</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MECIB-galapagos-andes-multi-adventure-tour-1.jpg'),(3150,'Croatia Walking & Hiking Tour &ndash; Older Teens & 20s','Dalmatian Coast Odyssey &ndash; Dubrovnik to Split',0,'Dubrovnik, Croatia','Split, Croatia','','It\'s usually a choice. Do you choose a destination with history, culture and natural beauty or do you go for sun, sea and a laid-back island atmosphere? Here it\'s both&mdash;the ideal blend of \"enlightenment\" and relaxation. When you come to the Dalmatian Coast, get set to enjoy two of the best vacations you\'ve ever had.','','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/WDCQ_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/19-map-WDCQ.jpg','Dalmatian Coast Croatia Map','Dalmatian Coast Walking Vacations','Dalmation Coast Croatia Map','Dalmation Coast Walking Vacations','<ul><li><strong>Explore </strong>the newly reborn Dalmatian Coast, gaining insight into Croatia\'s captivating history and distinctive culture</li><li><strong>Island-hop</strong> and swim in the sun-drenched Adriatic, including the secluded swimming oasis of Stracincica Bay</li><li><strong>Discover</strong> Dubrovnik, an architectural masterpiece with an impressive turrets and an 82-foot-high fortified wall</li><li><strong>Hike</strong> amid silver-green olive groves, lush undulating fields and dramatic rocky cliffs with jaw-dropping sea views</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/WDCQ-dalmatian-coast-walking-hiking-tour-1.jpg'),(3206,'Kauai Family Multi-Adventure Tour - Older Teens & 20s','Dramatic Hanalei Bay & Waimea Canyon',0,'Kapaa, Kauai','Poipu or Lihue, Kauai','','An adventuring family\'s tropical paradise, Kauai is one of