travel/images/maps/19-map-MUAIB.jpg','Maui Family Multi-Adventure Tour &ndash; Older Teens & 20s | Map','Maui Family Multi-Adventure Tour - Older Teens and Twenties','Map |  Maui Family Multi-Adventure Tour - Older Teens & 20s | Backroads','Maui Family Multi-Adventure Tour &ndash; Older Teens & 20s','<ul><li><strong>Hike </strong>through lush landscapes on island trails through the West Maui Mountains and Haleakala National Park</li><li><b>Paddle</b> alongside sea turtles, rays and dolphins as you kayak in the turquoise waters of Olowalu Reef</li><li><b>Journey</b> down Maui\'s famed eastern coastline on the dramatically beautiful road to Hana</li><li><b>Escape</b> to a tropical paradise with sandy beaches, superb dining and luxurious oceanfront hotels</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/MUAIB-maui-multi-adventure-tour-3.jpg'),(3208,'Kauai Family Multi-Adventure Tour - Teens & Kids','Dramatic Hanalei Bay & Waimea Canyon',0,'Kapaa, Kauai','Poipu or Lihue, Kauai','','An adventuring family\'s tropical paradise, Kauai is one of the most idyllic places on Earth. Hike its canyons, mountains and rain forest. Kayak and snorkel in its warm waters. Soak up its sunshine from the sand. Savor fresh island cuisine and relax at elegant oceanfront hotels. Discover the Garden Isle with your family. It\'s a journey in full bloom. ','','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/19-map-MKUIF.svg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/19-map-MKUIF.jpg','Kauai Family Multi-Adventure Tour &ndash; Teens & Kids | Map','Kauai Family Multi-Adventure Tour - Teens & Kids','Kauai Map','Kauai Family Multi-Adventure Tour - Teens & Kids','<ul><li><b>Hike</b> peaceful tropical trails through exotic fauna, lush valleys, pristine forest reserves and along dazzling coastline</li><li><b>Bliss</b> out on secluded beaches where golden sand meets inviting turquoise waters perfect