ill.','','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/BASI9_15_map_sm.jpg','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/maps/20_BASI9.jpg','Champagne & Alsace Family Bike Tour - 20s & Beyond Map','Champagne & Alsace Family Bike Tour - 20s & Beyond | Backroads','Champagne & Alsace Family Bike Tour - 20s & Beyond Map','Champagne & Alsace Family Bike Tour - 20s & Beyond | Backroads','<ul><li><strong>Enjoy </strong>an exclusive private dinner and champagne pairing at world-famous Moët & Chandon, the oldest Maison de Champagne</li><li><strong>Cycle</strong> by canals and through scenic towns on the famed Route des Vins, hugging the peaceful Vosges foothills</li><li><strong>Discover</strong> some of France\'s most beautiful villages, with half-timbered houses and gardens filled with colorful geraniums</li><li><strong>Experience </strong>in one of the most memorable dining events ever&mdash;two Michelin stars at the incomparable Auberge de l\'Ill</li></ul>','https://s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/professor.raupach/acme_travel/images/trips/BASI9D-champagne-alsace-bike-tour-1.jpg');
